{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Epic Hero Game is a physics-based roguelite / soulslike where you play as a superhero and its your job to save the world from an alien invasion where the world is getting totally destroyed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you fight through enemies, player gets stronger during the fight by absorbing energy of slain monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game uses physics as a backbone for ridiculous anime powerscaling, where you can physically see a difference in the combat, the more stronger you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081720/extras/ezgif-2-2894459e11.gif?t=1731359752\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081720/extras/9001__3_.gif?t=1731359752\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your own superhero and fight off against an alien invasion on the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defend the fully destructible map using a variety of skills, moves and abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avoid the destruction of the Map as best you can however more powerful abilities will be more risky. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Epic Hero game will take you on a vast journey through themed worlds where your new unique abilities will help you defend them all or not....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2081720?t=1731359752","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepageback